	</div>
	
	<section class="row faq breath">
		<div class="col-md-6">
			<h6>who are you?</h6>
			<p>i'm sahil gupta, sy '17, a yalie who loves people, food, and surprise. credit also goes to jenny allen, tc '16, who worked with me to conceptualize and code the first version of the app this summer</p>
