			<h6>how do you pair students?</h6>
			<p>with a depth-first search algorithm that matches students who are free at a common time and place, all while maximizing the total number of matches</p>
			<h6>feedback | questions?</h6>
			<p>reach me at <a href="mailto:pear.yale@gmail.com?subject=feedback">pear.yale@gmail.com</a>. i'll get back to you on the same day</p>
